<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Let's Gamble</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background-color: #f4f4f4;
    }

    header {
      background-color: #333;
      color: #fff;
      padding: 10px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    nav {
      background-color: #444;
      padding: 10px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    nav a {
      color: #fff;
      text-decoration: none;
      margin: 0 15px;
    }

    section {
      padding: 20px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <header>
    <header>
      <h1>Comibear's Gambling</h1>
    </header>
  </header>

  <nav>
    <a href="/">Home</a>
    <% if(isLoggedIn) { %>
      <a href="/logout">Logout</a>
    <% } else { %>
      <a href="/login">Login</a>
    <% } %>
    <a href="/users">Members</a>
    <a href="/chat">Chat</a>
  </nav>

  <section>
    <% if (isLoggedIn) { %>
      <h1>Welcome to the Gambling Website, <%= nickname%> user</h1>
    <% } else { %>
      <h1>Welcome to the Gambling Website, Please log in first.</h1>
    <% } %></h1>
    <h2>Rule Book</h2>
    <p>1. First if you log in, Each user will be allocated 100,000 dollars.</p>
    <p>2. Each user can bring other users' money through the game.</p>
    <p>3. If you go into the members, it's ranked based on money, so try to win first place!!</p>
  </section>

</body>
</html>
